    {
      "paragraph_name": "COPAU0AO",
      "summary": null,
      "purpose": "This paragraph defines the data structure COPAU0AO, which redefines COPAU0AI. It provides an alternative view of the data, breaking down some of the fields into smaller components. Specifically, it redefines TRNNAMEF into TRNNAMEC, TRNNAMEP, TRNNAMEH, TRNNAMEV, and TRNNAMEO, and TITLE01F into TITLE01C, TITLE01P, TITLE01H, TITLE01V, and TITLE01O. This redefinition allows the program to access the same data in different formats, potentially for display or processing purposes. The 'C', 'P', 'H', and 'V' suffixes might represent different attributes or parts of the original fields.",
